<h3><a href="../../index.html">The Consumer Law Page</a>: <a href="../index.html">Articles</a>: <a href="fraud.shtml">CONSUMER FRAUD: Spotting and 
Protecting Yourself Against It [A General Primer]</a>:</h3>
