<h3>Defective Products</h3>
<hr>
<ul>
<li>All Terrain Vehicles -- <a href="http://www. seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/defect.html/talf/txt/atv.html">http://www.seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/defect.html/talf/txt/atv.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>ANSI American National Standards Institute -- <a href="http://www.ansi.org">http://www.ansi.org </a><img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>ARIAWeb American Risk and Insurance Association -- <a href="http://riskweb.utexas/aria.html">http://riskweb.utexas/aria.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Auto Safety Hotline 1-800-424-9393 (TTY for Hearing Impaired 1-800-424-9153) <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>The Better Business Bureau Web Server -- <a href="http://www.cbbb.org/cbbb">http://www.cbbb.org/cbbb</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Breast Implants: Fact v. Fiction in the Harvard and Mayo Clinic Studies -- 
<a href="http://www.seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/breast.html">http://www.seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/breast.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Breast Implants: New Evidence Against Dow Chemical -- 
<a href="http://www. seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/dow.html">http://www.seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/dow.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Center for Auto Safety, Washington D.C., (202-328-7700) <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Chemically Induced Asthma: Reactive Airways Dysfunctions Syndrome -- 
<a href="http://www.seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/asthma.html">http://www.seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/asthma.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Chemically Induced Diseases: Synergistic Effects and Cumulative Injuries caused by Toxic 
Chemicals -- Understanding the Gulf War Syndrome and Multiple Chemical Sensitivity [MCS] 
-- <a href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/gulfwar.html">http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/gulfwar.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Chrysler ABS Brakes Recall and Payback -- 
<a href="http://www.seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/absbrake.html">http://www.seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/absbrake.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Civil Justice: Provides information on legislation, studies, policy papers, and campaigns aimed at 
restricting victims' rights and weakening liability laws. <a href="mailto:ListProc@essential.org">ListProc@essential.org</a> (To subscribe, 
send e-mail to: listproc@essential.org and in the body write: subscribe civil-justice firstname 
lastname) <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Consumer Information Center -- <a href="http://www.gsa.gov/staff/pa/cic/cic.htm">http://www.gsa.gov/staff/pa/cic/cic.htm</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
