<li>The Trade Secrets Home Page -- <a href="http://www.execpc.com/~mhallign/">http://www.execpc.com/~mhallign/</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Tobacco, Nicotine and Addiction. The American Broadcasting Company's legal memorandum in support of its motion 
for summary judgment against Philip Morris Inc., discusses nicotine &quot;spiking&quot; of cigaretes and allegedly contradicts the 
testimony of Philip Morris executives before Congress -- <a href="http://www.courttv.com/download/library/tobacco/brief.html">http://www.courttv.com/download/library/tobacco/brief.html</a><img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Trademark Application Forms -- <a href="http://www.naming.com/naming/tmforms.html">http://www.naming.com/naming/tmforms.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
