<h3>Parenting and Family</h3>
<hr>
<ul>
<li>Adoption Assitance Information Support -- <a href="http://www.adopting.org/">http://www.adopting.org/</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Adoption Books for Children and Adults: The Tapestry Books site provides adoption related books for children and 
adults. Listings contain descriptions of books in many subject areas such as &quot;before you adopt,&quot; &quot;international adoption,&quot; 
&quot;adoption and families,&quot; &quot;open adoption,&quot; &quot;raising adopted children,&quot; &quot;especially for birthparents,&quot; &quot;teenage pregnancy&quot; and 
&quot;for professionals.&quot; -- <a href="http://www.webcom.com/tapestry">http://www.webcom.com/tapestry</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Adoption Fraud by Adoption Agencies -- <a href="http://www.seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/adopt.html">http://www.seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/adopt.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Adoption Law -- <a href="gopher://english.hss.cmu.edu:70/00ftp%3AEnglish.Server%3APower%3AAdoption%20">gopher://english.hss.cmu.edu:70/00ftp%3AEnglish.Server%3APower%3AAdoption%20</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>The Adventure Bonding Parenting Page -- <a href="http://www.imageplaza.com/parenting/">http://www.imageplaza.com/parenting/</a><img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Law American Academy of Pediatrics -- <a href="http://www.aap.org/dogl/dogl.html">http://www.aap.org/dogl/dogl.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Duke University Dept.of Community and Family Medicine -- <a href="http://dmi-www.mc.duke.edu/cfm/cfmhome.html">http://dmi-www.mc.duke.edu/cfm/cfmhome.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Infertility Books: The Tapestry Books site contains descriptions of books concerning &quot;learning about infertility,&quot; &quot;emotions 
and infertility&quot; and &quot;moving on.&quot; -- <a href="http://www.webcom.com/tapestry">http://www.webcom.com/tapestry</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Int'l Society for Child and Adolescent Injury Prevention -- <a href="http://weber.u.washin gton.edu:80/hiprc/iscaip.html">http://weber.u.washin gton.edu:80/hiprc/iscaip.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>National Center for Missing and Exploited Children -- <a href="http://www.missingkids.org/">http://www.missingkids.org/</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>National Resource Directory for Parents of children with special needs -- <a href="http://www.portal.com/~cbntmkr/php.html">http://www.portal.com/~cbntmkr/php.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Parenting Challenges: The Tapestry books listing contains descriptions of books about &quot;attention deficit disorder,&quot; 
&quot;behavioral problems&quot; and &quot;parenting issues.&quot; -- <a href="http://www.webcom.com/tapestry">http://www.webcom.com/tapestry</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Precious in HIS Sight -- Internet Adoption Photolisting -- <a href="http://nysernet.org/cyber/adoption">http://nysernet.org/cyber/adoption</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Taking Back Our Stolen Future:Hormone disruption [depletion of human sperm] and PVC plastic -- 
<a href="http://www.greenpeace.org/~uk/science/stolen.txt">http://www.greenpeace.org/~uk/science/stolen.txt</a><img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Tobacco, Nicotine and Addiction. The American Broadcasting Company's legal memorandum in support of its motion for 
summary judgment against Philip Morris Inc., discusses nicotine &quot;spiking&quot; of cigaretes and allegedly contradicts the 
testimony of Philip Morris executives before Congress -- <a href="http://www.courttv.com/download/library/tobacco/brief.html">http://www.courttv.com/download/library/tobacco/brief.html</a><img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Women and the Law -- <a href="http://holmes.law.cwru.edu/1/women+law">http://holmes.law.cwru.edu/1/women+law</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Women in the Law: Feminist Curricular Resources -- <a href="http://www.law.indiana.edu:80/fcrc/fcrc.html">http://www.law.indiana.edu:80/fcrc/fcrc.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>WomensNet -- <a href="http://www.igc.apc.org/womensnet/">http://www.igc.apc.org/womensnet/</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
</ul>
