<h3>Toxic Chemicals</h3>
<hr size=4 width=75%>
<ul>
<li>Agency for Toxic Substances and Disease Registry -- <a href="http://atsdr1.atsdr.cdc.gov:8080/atsdrhome.html">http://atsdr1.atsdr.cdc.gov:8080/atsdrhome.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>American Chemical Society -- <a href="gopher://acsinfo.acs.org">gopher://acsinfo.acs.org </a><img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>ARTICLE: Industry's &quot;True Lies&quot;: The Politics Behind the Scientific Debate on Dioxin: by Stephen U. Lester -- 
<a href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/truelies.html">http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/truelies.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>BOOK REVIEW: Designer Poisons: How to Protect Your Health and Home from Toxic Pesticides -- 
<a href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/designer.html">http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/designer.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Center for Bioenvironmental Research of Tulane and Xavier Universities in New Orleans -- 
<a href="http://www1.omi.tulane.edu/ecme/EEHome/6_Moreinfo/default.html">http://www1.omi.tulane.edu/ecme/EEHome/6_Moreinfo/default.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Center for Clean Technology at UCLA -- <a href="http://cct.seas.ucla.edu/">http://cct.seas.ucla.edu/</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Chemical Fact Sheets by Name at Case Western Reserve -- 
<a href="gopher://biochemistry.bioc.cwru.edu/7sc%3a/database/msds.mnu">gopher://biochemistry.bioc.cwru.edu/7sc%3a/database/msds.mnu</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Chemically Induced Diseases: Synergistic Effects and Cumulative Injuries caused by Toxic Chemicals -- Understanding 
the Gulf War Syndrome and Multiple Chemical Sensitivity [MCS] -- <a href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/gulfwar.html">http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/gulfwar.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Chemistry Index -- <a href="http://atf1.fagmed.uit.no/fagmed/chemistry.html">http://atf1.fagmed.uit.no/fagmed/chemistry.html </a><img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Chemical Safety Information -- <a href="http://pegasus.uthct.edu/ResUTHCT/MSDS/JTBaker/JTBaker.html">http://pegasus.uthct.edu/ResUTHCT/MSDS/JTBaker/JTBaker.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Chemistry Resources on the Internet -- <a href="http://www.rpi.edu/dept/chem/cheminfo/chemres.html">http://www.rpi.edu/dept/chem/cheminfo/chemres.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Chemical factsheets at the University of Virginia -- <a href="gopher://ecosys.drdr.Virginia.edu:70/11/library/gen/toxics">gopher://ecosys.drdr.Virginia.edu:70/11/library/gen/toxics</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Chemically Induced Asthma: Reactive Airways Dysfunctions Syndrome -- 
<a href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/asthma.html">http://www.seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/asthma.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Chemicals in the Environment: Fact Sheets -- <a href="http://www.epa.gov/docs/chemfact/">http://www.epa.gov/docs/chemfact/</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Citizens Clearinghouse for Hazardous Waste.-- <a href="http://www.essential.org/cchw">http://www.essential.org/cchw</a>. To receive updates on scientific and 
policy question about dioxin, link up with other dioxin activists and share your dioxin information, subscribe to the 
CCHW Dioxin Electronic Bulletin Board. Send the message &quot;subscribe dioxin-l [your name]&quot; to <a href="mailto:listproc@essential.org">listproc@essential.org</a> 
[be sure to put a space after &quot;dioxin-l&quot; in the subscribe message before your name]. For the CCHW home page open 
<a href="http://www.essential.org/orgs/CCHW/CCHW.html">http://www.essential.org/orgs/CCHW/CCHW.html</a> and e.mail at <a href="mailto:cchw@essential.org">cchw@essential.org</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Dioxin in Pentaclorophenol: A Case Study of Cancer Deaths in the Lumber Industry -- 
<a href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/lumber.html">http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/txt/lumber.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Drug and Toxic Chemical Fact Sheet by name at University of Virginia -- 
<a href="gopher://ecosys.drdr.virginia.edu/11/library/gen/toxics">gopher://ecosys.drdr.virginia.edu/11/library/gen/toxics </a><img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Endocrine Disruptors Research Initiative -- <a href="http://www.epa.gov/endocrine/">http://www.epa.gov/endocrine/</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Environmental Health Hazard Assessment -- <a href="http://www.cahwnet.gov/epa/oehha.htm">http://www.cahwnet.gov/epa/oehha.htm</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Environmental Information Center Global Issues -- <a href="http://www.eic.org/keyissue.html">http://www.eic.org/keyissue.html</a><img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Environmental Protection Agency, United States -- <a href="http://www.epa.gov">http://www.epa.gov</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Extension Toxicology Network -- <a href="http://ace.orst.edu/info/extoxnet/">http://ace.orst.edu/info/extoxnet/</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Extoxnet -- <a href="http://sulaco.oes.orst.edu: 70/1/ext/extoxnet">http://sulaco.oes.orst.edu: 70/1/ext/extoxnet</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Fisher Scientific (a chemical company; catalog of chemical products plus a list of chemistry-related web sites) -- 
<a href="http://www.fisher1.com">http://www.fisher1.com</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Guide to Federal Laboratory and Technology Related Resources -- 
<a href="gopher://sara.nalusda.gov:70/00/infocntr/ttic/t2guide.txt">gopher://sara.nalusda.gov:70/00/infocntr/ttic/t2guide.txt</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Gulf War Syndrome -- <a href="http://whyfiles.news.wisc.edu">http://whyfiles.news.wisc.edu</a><img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>HazardNet -- <a href="http://hoshi.cic.sfu.ca/hazard/">http://hoshi.cic.sfu.ca/hazard/</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
