<h3>Violence and Abuse Prevention</h3>
<hr>
<ul>
<li>Assault Prevention Information Network -- 
<a href="http://galaxy.einet.net/galaxy/Community/Safety/Assault-Prevention/apin/APIN/index.html">http://galaxy.einet.net/galaxy/Community/Safety/Assault-Prevention/apin/APIN/index.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Child Abuse and Neglect: National Data Archive -- <a href="gopher://gopher.ndacan.cornell.edu/">gopher://gopher.ndacan.cornell.edu/</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Domestic Violence Handbook -- <a href="http://www.interport.net/~asherman/toc.html">http://www.interport.net/~asherman/toc.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Domestic Violence Resources -- <a href="http://www.cybergrrl.com/dv.html">http://www.cybergrrl.com/dv.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>International Society for Child and Adolescent Injury Prevention -- <a href="http://weber.u.washington.edu:80/hiprc/iscaip.html">http://weber.u.washington.edu:80/hiprc/iscaip.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Magid's Child Safety Online -- <a href="http://www.omix.com/magid/child.safety.online.html">http://www.omix.com/magid/child.safety.online.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>National Center for Missing and Exploited Children -- <a href="http://www.missingkids.org/">http://www.missingkids.org/</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>Partnerships Against Violence NETwork (PAVNET) [anti-violence programs] -- 
<a href="gopher://cyfer.esusda.gov:70/11/violence">gopher://cyfer.esusda.gov:70/11/violence</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
<li>SafetyNet Domestic Violence Resources -- <a href="http://www.cybergrrl.com/dv.html">http://www.cybergrrl.com/dv.html</a> <img src="../pixel.gif" align=top width=1 height=25></li>
</ul>
