<h3 align=center>U.S. DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION<br>
Federal Highway Administration<br>
Report No. FHWA-PL-92-019<br>
</h3>
<h2 align=center>COST OF OWNING &amp; OPERATING<br>
Automobiles, Vans, and Trucks, 1991</h2>
<p>Prepared by:</p>
<p>Jack Faucett Associates<br>
4550 Montgomery Avenue<br>
Suite 300 North<br>
Bethesda, Maryland 20814<br>
In conjuction with<br>
Research and Special Programs Administration<br>
Volpe National Transportation Systems Center<br>
Center for Transportation Information<br>
Kendall Square<br>
Cambridge, Massachsetts 02142<br>
Prepared for<br>
Federal Highway Administration<br>
Office of Highway Information Management<br>
U.S. Department of Transportation<br>
washington, D.C. 20590<br>
