<h4><font color="#FF0000">Press </font><a href="http://consumerlawpage.com/nographics/brochure/97.shtml"><font color="#FF0000">here</font></a><font color="#FF0000"> for a &quot;no-graphics&quot; version of this page</font></h4>
<p><a href="../index.html#toxic"><img src="../article/../workers.gif" alt=" [Workers Injured By Toxics] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="../article/lenses.shtml"><img src="../lenses.gif" alt=" [Bausch &amp; Lomb Contact Lenses Class Action] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/nccc/cb-intro.html"><img src="../sm-nccc.gif" alt=" [National Consumer Complaint Center] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="../reserved.html"><img src="../reserved.gif" alt=" [Settlement Reached - GM Pickup Truck] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> 
<a href="../absgmc.html"><img src="../absgmc.gif" alt=" [GMC / Chevrolet Suburban ABS Brakes - Investigation] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="../fight.html"><img src="http://seamless.com/talf/fight-b.gif" alt=" [Consumers Fight Back!] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="../article/medtron.shtml"><img src="../consumers.gif" alt=" [Consumers Win In Supreme Court] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="../securities/index.html"><img src="../security.gif" alt="  [Securities &amp; Stocks Investor Fraud]  " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> 
<a href="../article/howhire.shtml"><img src="../finding.gif" alt=" [Finding the Right Lawyer]" align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="../article/fraud/fraud.shtml"><img src="../protect.gif" alt=" [Protect Yourself from Fraud] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="../article/nolan.shtml"><img src="../lawyer.gif" alt=" [Lawyer of the Month] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="../article/ibm.shtml"><img src="../ibm.gif" alt="[IBM Employees: Cancer Investigation]" align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> 
