<h2>Taxpayer and Consumer Quiz: Know Your Government</h2>
<h3>What does the Federal Food And Drug Administration Do For You?</h3>
<hr>
<p><font size=5>T</font>he Food and Drug Administration regulates a large number of consumer products important to you. But what exactly does it 
do? Take this informative quiz and find out just how many agencies of the U. S. government are involved in consumer health and 
safety.</p>
<p><font size=5>S</font>elect the one item in each of the following groups that is <strong>not</strong> under the jurisdiction of the Food and Drug Administration.</p>
<pre>

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="1">1</a>.      <a href="#right1">a</a>.      Spam
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      puppy food
        <a href="#wrong">c</a>.      chocolate-covered cherries
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      frozen spinach
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      imported caviar

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="2">2</a>.      <a href="#wrong">a</a>.      aspirin
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      anti-lice shampoo
        <a href="#right2">c</a>.      insect repellent
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      eye shadow
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      lipstick

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="3">3</a>.      <a href="#wrong">a</a>.      pesticide residues in lettuce
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      canned tomatoes
        <a href="#right3">c</a>.      oven cleaner
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      spaghetti
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      pet turtles

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="4">4</a>.      <a href="#wrong">a</a>.      airport security x-ray machines
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      laser products used in lumber mills
        <a href="#wrong">c</a>.      magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) diagnostic equipment
        <a href="#right4">d</a>.      smoke detectors
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      microwave ovens


<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="5">5</a>.      <a href="#wrong">a</a>.      TV sets
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      over-the-counter antacid
        <a href="#right5">c</a>.      TV ads for aspirin
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      diphtheria, pertussis and tetanus vaccine
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      human plasma


<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="6">6</a>.      <a href="#right6">a</a>.      baby pacifiers
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      baby bottles nipples
        <a href="#wrong">c</a>.      ceramic ware for food use
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      coffee mugs
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      eye chart

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="7">7</a>.      <a href="#right7">a</a>.      illegal heroin use
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      veterinary tetracycline
        <a href="#wrong">c</a>.      barbiturates
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      medicinal oxygen
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      methadone

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="8">8</a>.      <a href="#wrong">a</a>.      kidney dialysis machine
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      tongue depressor
        <a href="#wrong">c</a>.      toothpaste
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      fluoridated toothpaste
        <a href="#right8">e</a>.      hair dryer

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="9">9</a>.      <a href="#right9">a</a>.      label on beer
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      ground coffee
        <a href="#wrong">c</a>.      coffee beans
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      rabbit meat
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      canned tuna

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="10">10</a>.     <a href="#right10">a</a>.      home canning equipment
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      food warehouse
        <a href="#wrong">c</a>.      drug warehouse
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      hearing aid dispenser (retailer)
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      exporting of drugs

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="11">11</a>.     <a href="#wrong">a</a>.      Halloween make-up
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      theatrical make-up
        <a href="#right11">c</a>.      soap
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      eye mascara
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      nail polish

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="12">12</a>.     <a href="#right12">a</a>.      vaccine for horses
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      penicillin for horses
        <a href="#wrong">c</a>.      medicated feed for hogs
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      pet parrots
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      bird feed

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="13">13</a>.     <a href="#right13">a</a>.      tap water
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      club soda
        <a href="#wrong">c</a>.      bottled mineral water
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      ginger ale
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      bottled water for water cooler

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="14">14</a>.     <a href="#wrong">a</a>.      tamper-resistant packaging for over-the-counter (over the counter) drugs
        <a href="#right14">b</a>.      child-proof packaging for over the counter drugs
        <a href="#wrong">c</a>.      plastic containers for soft drinks
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      valentine heart containing chocolates
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      a tube containing medical ointment

<hr>NOT under FDA jurisdiction:

<a name="15">15</a>.     <a href="#right15">a</a>.      grooming cream for dogs
        <a href="#wrong">b</a>.      artificial limb for dogs
        <a href="#wrong">c</a>.      laser scanner at supermarket checkout
        <a href="#wrong">d</a>.      mercury vapor lamps
        <a href="#wrong">e</a>.      vitamin C tablets
</pre>
